---
title: Slippery Slimy Pork Spaghetti Worms with Cheese and Baby Spinach
description: These Slippery Slimy Pork Spaghetti Worms are a crowd pleaser and one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
